  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/ef9138f34e31a671f449b9ce10a37569.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=238 /></span><br><br>Unleash chaos in Voidigo, a vividly animated roguelite shooter packed with dynamic boss battles, zany weapons, and playful humor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/dc014c59889829a9baba3cae2a95be70.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=239 /></span><br><br>Select from an array of ranged and melee weapons to combat the looming corruption. Master the art of dodging and stun your enemies with stomps to tip the balance in your favor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/c38a5ccaed164bda87786228ae7f5f92.poster.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/c38a5ccaed164bda87786228ae7f5f92.webm?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/c38a5ccaed164bda87786228ae7f5f92.mp4?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/deacc914b9aac4feb2eea98702a65fae.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=239 /></span><br><br>Voidigo's numerous bosses, corrupted by the void, offer fierce resistance. They may flee mid-battle, giving you a choice: pursue or regroup. However, hesitate too long, and they'll begin hunting you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/a118ee94106e849afd3f32e82863d01d.poster.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/a118ee94106e849afd3f32e82863d01d.webm?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/a118ee94106e849afd3f32e82863d01d.mp4?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/41a5a83535a6792f006d7c97f10e82cf.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=239 /></span><br><br>In your battle, collect diverse power-ups for exciting synergies. Trade weapons and resources to customize your playstyle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/5570faac040cb01984026304beb267fb.poster.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/5570faac040cb01984026304beb267fb.webm?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/5570faac040cb01984026304beb267fb.mp4?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/ef9138f34e31a671f449b9ce10a37569.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=238 /></span><br><br>Unleash chaos in Voidigo, a vividly animated roguelite shooter packed with dynamic boss battles, zany weapons, and playful humor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/dc014c59889829a9baba3cae2a95be70.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=239 /></span><br><br>Select from an array of ranged and melee weapons to combat the looming corruption. Master the art of dodging and stun your enemies with stomps to tip the balance in your favor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/c38a5ccaed164bda87786228ae7f5f92.poster.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/c38a5ccaed164bda87786228ae7f5f92.webm?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/c38a5ccaed164bda87786228ae7f5f92.mp4?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/deacc914b9aac4feb2eea98702a65fae.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=239 /></span><br><br>Voidigo's numerous bosses, corrupted by the void, offer fierce resistance. They may flee mid-battle, giving you a choice: pursue or regroup. However, hesitate too long, and they'll begin hunting you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/a118ee94106e849afd3f32e82863d01d.poster.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/a118ee94106e849afd3f32e82863d01d.webm?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/a118ee94106e849afd3f32e82863d01d.mp4?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/41a5a83535a6792f006d7c97f10e82cf.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=239 /></span><br><br>In your battle, collect diverse power-ups for exciting synergies. Trade weapons and resources to customize your playstyle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/5570faac040cb01984026304beb267fb.poster.avif?t=1773305310\" width=616 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/5570faac040cb01984026304beb267fb.webm?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304680/extras/5570faac040cb01984026304beb267fb.mp4?t=1773305310\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
